    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ここ……は？　洋服屋さん……でしょうか？\nそれにしてはいろんなものが売ってるような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is this place…? Is it a clothing store…?\nBut they seem to sell many other things too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.6041274547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "コスプレ衣装の専門店やで！\nずっと来てみたかったんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a store for cosplay costumes!\nI've always wanted to come here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.300000445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.8905215422
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "へー、こんなお店があったのね。衣装以外にも\n布や髪の毛に武器？　まで売ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ I didn't know there was a place like this. They sell\nfabric‚ hair‚ and even weapons…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.6238546211
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "それは髪の毛じゃなくてウィッグって言うんよ\nコスプレの必需品やね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not hair‚ it's called a wig.\nIt's essential for cosplay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.220699895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.4438771723
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ早速、二人はこの衣装に着替えて下さい\n沙季ちゃんはダラーテ、瑠依ちゃんはペト君です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ you two‚ please go change into these costumes now.\nSaki-chan will be Darlatte‚ and Rui-chan will be Peto-kun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1666668573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.4112695851
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待って！？　早速って何！？\n私と沙季がコスプレするの？　優は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on!? What do you mean \"now\"!?\nYou're saying Saki and I are going to cosplay? What about you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4000001906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.8446029184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ～。うちは今日のために買った\nこの一眼レフカメラに二人の姿を収めるんや～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu~. I'm going to capture you both with this\nDSLR camera I bought just for this occasion!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.0666668573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.8246477284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "嘘でしょ……。てっきり優がするのかとばかり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're kidding… I just assumed you were going to do it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8246477284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.8579836049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "二人にコスプレしてもらえる機会なんて今日しか\nないやん。うちはやろうと思えばいつでも出来るし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't have another chance to make you two cosplay\nfor me‚ you know! I can do it whenever I want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9666694004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.6592984038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ダメ……やろか？\nうちのために……これ着てくれへん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Would you say… no?\nCouldn't you wear it… for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.5333360671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.0741052148
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.8666668573
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました。優ちゃんのために一肌脱ぎます\n瑠依さん、一緒にやりましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay. I'll lend you my helping hand‚ Yu.\nRui‚ let's do it together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3666694004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ……優の誕生日だものね\nええ、分かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Well… It is your birthday‚ Yu.\nFine‚ I understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0829155891,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8950.417934800002,
          "startTime": 98.0333335239
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.1508848347
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "きゃ～～～～っ！　嬉しいわぁ～！\nさぁさぁっ！　それでは、こちらの試着室へ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kya～～～～! I'm so happy～!\nAlright‚ alright~! Then‚ to the fitting rooms…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0666694004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.600003751
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――瑠依と沙季が試着室に入って数十分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several tens of minutes after Rui and Saki entered the fitting rooms",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9774648504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.9374649362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ着替え終わりました～？\nもういいですか～？　覗いていいですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you guys done changing~?\nIs it okay now? Can I have a look?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4619105812,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4003.9257685999983,
          "startTime": 109.4658363498
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いいわよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.4658363498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.7658363498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "いやぁ～～～。無理無理無理無理！　無理です！\nダラーテとペトが現実世界にいるこの現実が無理です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my~~~. No‚ no‚ no‚ no! No way!\nThe reality of Darlatte and Peto being in the real world is no way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2387866974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんね、優。コスプレも男装も初めてで……\nそんなに無理な仕上がりだったかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry‚ Yu. This is my first time cosplaying and crossdressing…\nDid I really turn out that bad for you to say 'no way'…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.2000001906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.3392322059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "違います、違うんです、いい意味で無理なんです\nはあっ、瑠依ちゃんも沙季ちゃんも最高や、美し過ぎる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ that's not what I mean! I meant 'no way' in a good way!\nAhh‚ Rui-chan and Saki-chan‚ you both look amazing! So beautiful!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.5999976474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、優ちゃんが喜んでくれて良かったです\nこほんっ。「俺達は戦いの中でしか生きられない」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I'm glad you're happy‚ Yu-chan.\nAhem. \"We can only live within the throes of battle.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1999976474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.7724847153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "あ～っ！　原作24話で妹を亡くして絶望している\nペト君に、ダラーテが投げかけた名ゼリフ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! Darlatte's famous line to Peto-kun in episode 24‚\nwhen he was in despair after he lost his sister!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.1333350497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "ここから敵同士だった二人の関係は\n一気に加速するんよ……思い出しただけで涙が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From here‚ their relationship as enemies\ntook a dramatic turn… Just remembering it brings tears to my eyes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.4666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.6239803946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
