      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 354.9528671893
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……。やるなら、ちゃんとオーディション受けて\n自分の実力で勝ち取ってりんごさんと共演したいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… If I'm going to do it‚ I want to work with Ringo-san\nafter properly auditioning and winning the role with my own ability.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 358.5333411531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 363.6670848202
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、沙季ちゃん、りんごさん、スタッフさん\nせっかくうちのために用意してくれたのにすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui‚ Saki-san‚ Ringo-san‚ everyone on staff‚\nI'm sorry‚ even though you all went through the trouble of preparing this for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 369.0000078198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 373.9619823447
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu025.m4a",
      "text": "りんごさんに会えただけで、本当に本当に嬉しいです\n素敵なプレゼントありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just being able to meet Ringo-san is enough. I'm really‚ truly happy.\nThank you for the wonderful present.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 379.1000078198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝日りんご",
      "speakerNameEn": "Asahi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "分かりました。優ちゃんのそういうところ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. That's what I love",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 382.8944988878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝日りんご",
      "speakerNameEn": "Asahi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大好きです！　いつか絶対に共演しましょうね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "about you! Let's definitely work together someday!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 385.7963708487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 389.9889655422
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu026.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　あの……そのかわり一つだけお願いがあって\n……セリフを言ってもらうことって出来ますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Um… Instead‚ could I ask you for one thing?\n…Could you say a line for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 397.2333411531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 401.1348609915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝日りんご",
      "speakerNameEn": "Asahi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もちろんです！　優ちゃん、お誕生日おめでとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! Happy birthday‚ Yu-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 401.1348609915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝日りんご",
      "speakerNameEn": "Asahi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「僕を残してお前が死ぬことは許さない」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"I won't forgive you if you die and leave me behind.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 406.3000078198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 409.8377384812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu027.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～～耳が幸せ過ぎる……生きてて良かった……\nうち、もっともっと頑張ります～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh~ My ears are so blessed… I'm so glad to be alive…\nI'm going to work even harder~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 415.4666724519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 419.7418346873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu028.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、今日は一日うちに付き合ってくれて\nほんまにありがとう。最高の誕生日でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You two‚ thank you so much for spending the day\nwith me. It was the best birthday ever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 424.9666724519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 429.3734811773
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんが一番喜んでくれるプレゼントって\nなんだろう～って瑠依さんと考えたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-san and I wondered what kind of present\nwould make you happiest‚ Yu-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 432.3333391186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 435.3792508752
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "サプライズ喜んでくれて良かったわ\nそう言えば今日、『もんバケ』単行本の発売日よね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad you liked the surprise.\nThat reminds me‚ today's the release date for the new Monbake volume‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 439.2333391186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 443.6792508752
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "そうでした！　いいとこで終わってたんですよね……\n優ちゃん、本屋さん寄って帰りません？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! It ended on such a cliffhanger…\nYu-chan‚ do you want to stop by the bookstore on the way home?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 448.0000057853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 451.0718685458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_03-yu029.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ。もちろん！　星見プロにオタク仲間が\n出来そうなことがうちにとって一番のプレゼントやわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu. Of course! Having otaku buddies at Hoshimi Pro\nis the greatest present for me.",
